 come casa vostra, in uno stile semplice e accogliente.'),(2613,11,'_description_block_sx','field_6501c6b31cc53'),(2614,11,'button_block_sx',''),(2615,11,'_button_block_sx','field_6541029f71147'),(2616,11,'link_block_sx',''),(2617,11,'_link_block_sx','field_654102b571148'),(2618,11,'image_block_sx','116'),(2619,11,'_image_block_sx','field_653918277f014'),(2620,124,'subtitle_block_sx',''),(2621,124,'_subtitle_block_sx','field_6501c6a71cc52'),(2622,124,'title_block_sx',''),(2623,124,'_title_block_sx','field_6501c6891cc51'),(2624,124,'description_block_sx',''),(2625,124,'_description_block_sx','field_6501c6b31cc53'),(2626,124,'button_block_sx',''),(2627,124,'_button_block_sx','field_6541029f71147'),(2628,124,'link_block_sx',''),(2629,124,'_link_block_sx','field_654102b571148'),(2630,124,'image_block_sx',''),(2631,124,'_image_block_sx','field_653918277f014'),(2632,196,'image_header',''),(2633,196,'_image_header','field_65006caf46349'),(2634,196,'title_header','Contatti'),(2635,196,'_title_header','field_65006d214634a'),(2636,196,'description_header','Small is a dedicated performance management platform that helps you execute on your strategic goals and retain key talent. You need to give managers the power to drive employee performance in alignment with your strategic objectives.'),(2637,196,'_description_header','field_6501d77154f45'),(2638,196,'button_header','Scopri di più'),(2639,196,'_button_header','field_65006d2b4634b'),(2640,196,'button_fixed_course','Scopri i nostri corsi'),(2641,196,'_button_fixed_course','field_65006d914634c'),(2642,196,'title_bloc1','Contattaci'),(2643,196,'_title_bloc1','field_65392dfab35b4'),(2644,196,'description_bloc1','Establish clear goals, align on priorities and monitor progress throughout your organisation. Establish'),(2645,196,'_description_bloc1','field_65392dfab6fdf'),(2646,196,'titoletto_riferimenti_contatto','CONTATTACI'),(2647,196,'_titoletto_riferimenti_contatto','field_65392e398d529'),(2648,196,'riferimenti_contatti','Via P